sequenceDiagram
  participant Reed as Reed switch
  participant ESP as ESP32 publisher
  participant MQ as Mosquitto broker
  participant Dash as Dashboard subscriber
  participant Op as Operador

  Reed->>ESP: Cambio fisico abierto/cerrado
  ESP->>ESP: Debounce de 60 ms
  ESP->>MQ: publish sensor/compartment/N
  ESP->>MQ: publish sensor/summary
  MQ-->>Dash: entrega mensajes suscritos
  Dash->>Dash: actualiza snapshot y eventos
  Dash->>MQ: publish actuator/alarm
  Dash-->>Op: actualiza interfaz en tiempo real
  Op->>Dash: reconocer alarma o cambiar monitoreo
  Dash->>MQ: publish command/set-monitoring
  MQ-->>ESP: comando MQTT
  ESP->>ESP: habilita o inhibe alarma local
